form.current-chamber: IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES

action.action-desc: Received; read twice and referred to the Committee on Homeland Security and Governmental Affairs

form.official-title: To designate the facility of the United States Postal Service located at 101 East Market Street in Long Beach, California, as the Juanita Millender-McDonald Post Office.

subsection.text: The facility of the United States Postal Service located at 101 East Market Street in Long Beach, California, shall be known and designated as the Juanita Millender-McDonald Post Office.

Any reference in a law, map, regulation, document, paper, or other record of the United States to the facility referred to in section 1 shall be deemed to be a reference to the Juanita Millender-McDonald Post Office.

attestation-group.attestation-date: Passed the House of Representatives December 8, 2014.
